<item>
            <title>[SOLR-13568] Expand component should not cache group queries in the filter cache</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-13568</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the expand component is creating queries (bit sets) from the current page document ids.&lt;br/&gt;
These queries are sadly put in the filter cache.&lt;br/&gt;
This behavior floods the filter cache and it becomes inefficient.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the group query should be wrapped in a query with its cache flag disabled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a tiny little thing to do. The PR will follow very soon.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
